cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DB, cs.CL, cs.IR. 

The paper proposes a model for knowledge base completion, which is a task related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The model is based on TransR, which is a model for knowledge representation and reasoning, and is therefore related to databases (cs.DB). The evaluation of the model is done on the task of entity prediction, which involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
